         Morty says stop giving weaps to your pet at 39.</P><P>I had a 29 pet up in Tizmak caves the other day and he wasn't dual wielding very often. Then we gave him a couple of velium weaps and it seemed like he was doing better, plus the weapons would proc every once in a while (12 dmg - uber). Maybe it was just the primary that procced, not sure.</P><P>I haven't parsed the log yet so I can't say for certain that it made a big difference, but it sure seemed like it at the time.</P><P>It was actually kind of a fun group - me with a 26-hitter pet, a 39 wiz, a 30 shammy and a 34 mage with an air pet. The pets did all the tanking, and the mage was complaining (jokingly) because my pet was taking aggro every fight even with taunt off.</P><P>Smyrt Bertoxxnik, 32 Gnecro, Vaz</P><P>Edited by - Smyrt on 07/18/2002  13:06:57<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
