         Pets don't auto DW until 39, give it 2 weapons from 29-39 to insure it does.</P><P>mobs tend to attack the closest mob to it (on raids the MT will run right up to the mob and everyone else told to attack from max range, there is a reason); necro pets tend to have a smaller melee range then mage pets, so yours will be closer and get the agro.  also, are you sure their pet had taunt on?  the only mage pet i've seen that holds agro over mine with taunt off is epic.</P><P><a href="http://www.theinverselogic.com/" target="_blank"><BR>Abillister "Monkey" Abu<BR>Inverse Logic</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
